Hey Atul â€” not sure if you figured  this out or not yet, but you will either have to use the <https://github.HubSpot.com/cms-react/reference/cms-components.html#menu|helper component> or if you want you can roll your own menu component by using something along the lines of
```// module index.js file
// <http://module.menu|module.menu> references the menu field

export const hublDataTemplate = `
  {% set hublData = {
      "navigation" : menu(<http://module.menu|module.menu>, "site_root")
    }
  %}
`;```
You will then see the navigation items under `props.hublData.navigation`
